excerpt.rendered:
LB1 is entry-level dimmable LED bulb. With its powerful and smart core, you can easily switch on and off via your
smart phone from anywhere, change the brightness or color, schedule it to automatically power on and off as
needed. Besides, you can free your hands and control it directly with the voice commands when paired with a
compatible Amazon Echo or Google Nest device.
LB1 is suitable for the lamps of your bedroom, kitchen, study and so on. It greatly brings smart and convenience
